<!-- 
The template for a tile description text

Used to compute the description text shown in Template:fluidops:TileDescription
The description is retrieved from the rdfs:comment of the passed URI (or the 
current page)

Note: the description is retrieved from the config repository

	the parameter {{{pageName}}} - the name (URI resolvable) of the page (optional, default current page)


Example usage on "include:DatacentersTile"

description={{Template:fluidops:TileDescriptionText|pageName=include:DatacentersTile}}


-->
{{#show: {{{pageName|{{this}} }}} | rdfs:comment | valueResolver=DEFAULT_NOERROR | repository=config}}